positions of the mapped reads d corresponds to the size of
the sequenced fragment. In order to assign read pairs to the
un-ligated category, we use an upper size threshold that should
reflect the maximum credible size of sonified fragments.

positions of the mapped reads d plus the calculated size d' of the hybrid
